{"tid":2090903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外交部趙立堅：蓬佩奧之流不懂國際關係 天天撒謊造謠","createTime":"2020-07-02T11:46:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T16:21:33.000Z","uid":7542,"like":126,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac2a6d5d939e38a310e4142396412140fecc3f6","tid":2090903,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:46:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>戰狼終於有新嘅鬧人方法 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院通過《香港自治法案》，容許對參與實施「港區國安法」的中國官員實施制裁，懲罰與他們有業務往來的銀行。在北京，外交部對美國國會執意計劃推進有關涉港消極議案，表示強烈不滿及堅決反對，美方阻撓中方推進實施港區國安法的圖謀注定失敗。對於美國國務卿蓬佩奧批評北京將一國兩制變成一國一制，發言人趙立堅反指蓬佩奧日日撒謊及造謠，充分曝露他對港區國安法、對一國兩制、對中英聯合聲明，以及對國際法與國際關係基本原理的無知。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅指出，蓬佩奧之流之所以跳得這麼高，是因為他們不能夠再好像過去一樣為所欲為，肆無忌憚地破壞中國主權及安全，法例為香港加裝防盜門，必將引領香港重回正軌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535461-20200702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535461-20200702.htm&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8D2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=b11d4f23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1535461-20200702.htm&h=8c12926d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1535461-20200702.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xbFFY9CPduw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxbFFY9CPduw&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8D2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=7e7ee48b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xbFFY9CPduw</a>"},{"pid":"c269f57f6174f35773741e36ceb18c3aa2f2e637","tid":2090903,"uid":183090,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"要拉𨳊蓬佩奧，竟然觸犯天朝律例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823cbb8906a573e205f009439ed4347a7fdd76f4","tid":2090903,"uid":12558,"li